<Window x:Class="GUI_2022_23_01_UHPYQ8.YourName"
        xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
        xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
        xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008"
        xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006"
        xmlns:local="clr-namespace:GUI_2022_23_01_UHPYQ8"
        mc:Ignorable="d"
        Title="YourName" Height="450" Width="800"
        Closing="Window_Closing"
        WindowState="Maximized"
        Cursor="Cursors/minato_normal_select_animated.ani">
    <Window.Resources>
        <FontFamily x:Key="naruto" >/Fonts/#Ninja Naruto</FontFamily>
        <ImageBrush x:Key="Brush" ImageSource="MenuBackground/ecset2.png"></ImageBrush>
        <ImageBrush x:Key="BrushBlack" ImageSource="MenuBackground/ecset1.png"></ImageBrush>

    </Window.Resources>
    <Grid>
        <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
            <ColumnDefinition Width="1*"></ColumnDefinition>
            <ColumnDefinition Width="1*"></ColumnDefinition>
        </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
        <Grid>
            <Grid.Background>
                <ImageBrush ImageSource="MenuBackground/NameBackground.png"></ImageBrush>
            </Grid.Background>
            <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                <ColumnDefinition Width="1.1*"></ColumnDefinition>
                <ColumnDefinition Width="3.2*"></ColumnDefinition>
                <ColumnDefinition Width="1.1*"></ColumnDefinition>
            </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
            <Grid Grid.Column="1">
                <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                    <RowDefinition Height="1*"></RowDefinition>
                    <RowDefinition Height="20*"></RowDefinition>
                    <RowDefinition Height="40*"></RowDefinition>
                    <RowDefinition Height="1*"></RowDefinition>
                </Grid.RowDefinitions>
                <Viewbox Grid.Row="1">
                    <Label Content="Game Rules" HorizontalAlignment="Center" VerticalAlignment="Top" FontSize="40" FontFamily="{StaticResource naruto}" Background="{x:Null}" Foreground="#FF151515"></Label>
                </Viewbox>
                <Viewbox Grid.Row="2" HorizontalAlignment="Center" VerticalAlignment="Center">
                    <TextBlock FontFamily="Arial" TextWrapping="Wrap"> 
                        <LineBreak></LineBreak>
                        <Bold>Short Game Controller Guide</Bold>
                        <LineBreak></LineBreak>
                        <LineBreak></LineBreak>
                        The main goal in this game is to survive.<LineBreak></LineBreak>
                        Shurikens come and go and you have to <LineBreak></LineBreak>
                        dodge these shurikens with jumping.
                        <LineBreak></LineBreak><LineBreak></LineBreak>
                        - You can jump with <Bold>[SPACE]</Bold> button.<LineBreak></LineBreak>
                        <LineBreak></LineBreak>
                        Another difficulty of the game is that the enemy uses - Water Style -<LineBreak></LineBreak>
                        jutsu against us.<LineBreak></LineBreak>
                        To protect yourself against water you must use fire.<LineBreak></LineBreak>
                        <LineBreak></LineBreak>
                        - You can use - Fire style - jutsu with <Bold>[1]</Bold> button.<LineBreak></LineBreak>    
                        <LineBreak></LineBreak>    
                        <Bold>In summary</Bold>:<LineBreak></LineBreak><LineBreak></LineBreak>
                        - You will control <Bold>Uchia Madara</Bold>, who is one of the strongest shinobi ever.<LineBreak></LineBreak>
                        <LineBreak></LineBreak>
                       -  If shuriken comes, you have to jump, otherwise you have to use fire.<LineBreak></LineBreak>
                        <LineBreak></LineBreak>
                       -  As the game progresses, the game will speed up
                       -  due to the music.<LineBreak></LineBreak>
                        <LineBreak></LineBreak>
                       -  You have <Bold>four health</Bold>, which you can see in the upper left corner.<LineBreak></LineBreak>
                        <LineBreak></LineBreak>
                       - You can quit at any time with <Bold>[ESC]</Bold> Menu button.<LineBreak></LineBreak>
                        <LineBreak></LineBreak>
                       - You can skip the intro with <Bold>[ENTER]</Bold> button.
                        <LineBreak></LineBreak><LineBreak></LineBreak><LineBreak></LineBreak><LineBreak></LineBreak>

                    </TextBlock>
                </Viewbox>
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
    </Grid>
</Window>
